604
00:27:35.571 --> 00:27:38.032
It means...

605
00:27:38.115 --> 00:27:40.743
You know. well. well. it mea...
[sighs] It means...

606
00:27:40.826 --> 00:27:43.162
[sighs] I'm not good
at this sort of thing. I...

607
