-How do I look?

659
00:30:31.288 --> 00:30:32.498
How are... [chuckles]

660
00:30:32.581 --> 00:30:34.100
Fabulous as ever.
How's your lovely lady wife?

661
00:30:34.124 --> 00:30:36.252
She is around.

662
00:30:36.335 --> 00:30:37.962
Oh...

663
