711
00:33:40.894 --> 00:33:41.895
[Ian] Debbie.

712
00:33:41.979 --> 00:33:43.856
[chuckles]

713
00:33:43.939 --> 00:33:46.567
Good Lord. Steady on.

714
00:33:46.650 --> 00:33:47.776
Piss off. Ian.

715
00:33:47.860 --> 00:33:49.027
What?

716
00:33:49.737 --> 00:33:51.280
Piss off.

