752
00:35:22.704 --> 00:35:25.916
I have kept this marriage afloat
every day.

753
00:35:25.999 --> 00:35:27.876
I carried him every step of the way.

754
00:35:27.960 --> 00:35:29.878
every step of the way.

755
00:35:29.962 --> 00:35:32.273
